                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090517-58-off340 t18090517-58-cd341"></join>, three quarters of a yard of woollen cloth, value 3 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18090517-58-victim573" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Gilpin
               <interp inst="t18090517-58-victim573" type="surname" value="Gilpin"></interp>
